@endnode
@node Legal "Legal"

This script is freeware. On the grounds that a lot of my scripts are based
on at least parts of someone else's I'm not even going to copyright the
bits of it that Roy didn't write.

However, I ask that anyone improving this script lets @{"me" link Auth} have a copy before
it's widely released. This is so that I can coordinate the release of a
single 'super' script, rather than a set of slightly different variations
on a theme. I have no intentions of stealing credit for improving things :)

@endnode
